#

Garlic Butter Shrimp with Asparagus

$18.5
350 kcal

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Low CarbHigh Protein

Tags:

SeafoodQuick MealHealthy

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed in a rich garlic butter sauce, served with tender asparagus for a delightful and quick meal.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Asparagus (trimmed): 1 bunch
  • Garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Red pepper flakes: 1/2 tsp (optional)
